@startuml Skills Architecture
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam componentStyle uml2

title Skills Architecture and Activation Flow

package "Skills Repository\n(~/.copilot/skills/)" as Repo #LightBlue {
  component [architect] as Architect #LightGreen
  component [dev-workflow] as DevWorkflow #LightGreen
  component [mcp-builder] as McpBuilder #LightGreen
  component [pdf] as Pdf #LightGreen
  component [recursive-context] as RecursiveContext #LightGreen
  component [sys-env] as SysEnv #LightGreen
  component [web-scraper] as WebScraper #LightGreen
}

package "OpenCode Platform\n(~/.config/opencode/skills/)" as OpenCode #LightYellow

actor "Conversation Start" as Conversation #LightCoral

Repo --> OpenCode : sync-skills.sh
OpenCode --> Conversation : activate_all.py\n(validates & loads)

note right of OpenCode
  Automatic activation
  at conversation start.
  AI uses skills autonomously.
end note

note right of Repo
  Central hub for all skills.
  Managed with Git & CI/CD.
end note

@enduml